cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.SY

Reasoning: 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on the control of a wall following robot using machine learning models. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper presents a comparative study on the performance of different machine learning algorithms. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with the use of machine learning models for control. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is a less likely category as the paper does not explicitly mention any image processing or computer vision techniques. However, ultrasound sensors can be considered as a form of sensing and perception, which falls under the domain of computer vision. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is also a less likely category as the paper focuses more on the machine learning aspect rather than the control theory aspect.
